wake up exhausted.

00:01:59.244 --> 00:02:02.288 position:50% align:center
Then perhaps our adventure
is wearing you down.

00:02:02.372 --> 00:02:04.290 position:50% align:center
We'd better spend
today relaxing.

00:02:08.044 --> 00:02:10.130 position:50% align:center
[LETTY snoring]

00:02:11.423 --> 00:02:14.426 position:50% align:center
